how to play multiplayer games on wii well me and my dad are playin the wii and i was wanderin how do u connect another wii remoted to the wii so we can both play mario party well first try turning on the controller and see if it will automatically connect if not this should work press the home button the one with the little blue house between the and buttons and look at the bottom of the screen and click on the wii remote settings select reconnect and then it will tell you how to connect your remotes press and simultaneously on both remotes to connect them and then hit ok have fun Mouse (computing) Nintendo GameCube Windows XP Computer and video games Super Mario Bros. 3 Xbox Nintendo DS Beatmania IIDX PlayStation Portable Gradius Final Fantasy: Crystal Chronicles IPod Screenshot Dance Dance Revolution Mario Kart DS Multiplayer Dance Dance Revolution EXTREME WarioWare, Inc.: Mega Party Game$ Nintendo Entertainment System Daigasso! Band Brothers Dance Dance Revolution EXTREME (North America) Day of Defeat DDRMAX: Dance Dance Revolution GoldenEye 007 Game controller DDRMAX2: Dance Dance Revolution 7thMIX Dance Dance Revolution ULTRAMIX Halo: Combat Evolved Dance Dance Revolution 4thMIX DDRMAX: Dance Dance Revolution 6thMIX Nintendo Revolution Pump It Up Dance Dance Revolution ULTRAMIX 2 Super Mario 64 DS Slot machine Poker jargon Game Boy Dungeons & Dragons: Shadow over Mystara Remote control Mario Nintendo Super Mario Bros. Starsiege: Tribes Pop'n Music Computer and video game genres PlayStation 2 Super Mario 64 Team Fortress Classic AmigaOS Super Mario Advance 4 Xbox 360 Game Boy Advance DDRMAX2: Dance Dance Revolution Key telephone system Game Boy Player Danger Hiptop Homestar Runner Halo 2 X10 (industry standard) Game show Minesweeper (computer game) Guilty Gear Super Mario Kart Metroid Prime: Hunters Quake III Arena Console game Sega Mega Drive/Sega Genesis Sega Saturn Counter-Strike Shun Goku Satsu Worms weapons and tools Wave Race: Blue Storm Half-Life Diablo I